Version 3.4
    * changed "queue" to use standard ISOs instead of LVM templates
    * fixed Debian remove_packages bug
    * added preliminary fedora support

Version 3.3
    * added initial support for alternate (install) disc creation
    * minor bug fixes
    * added support for removing packages from the live environment (--remove-packages)
    * changed option for adding packages (--add-packages)
    * fixed bug with unmounting temporary partitions

Version 3.2.4
    * fixed bug with /proc and /dev/pts not being unmounted properly


